    "updated_at": "2014-09-09T03:52:12Z",
    "body": "Node's `Buffer` seems to have mistaken WebKit's external string for `Buffer`, before I find a way to fix this, you can force converting WebKit's external string to pure JavaScript string by `str1 = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(str1))` to work around it.\n"
